title: AtmosFEARfx 5 dvds ripped to MKVs
description:
These are 5 dvds that available at most Spirit stores.  Unliving Portraits, Ghostly Apparitions, Zombie Invasion, Bone Chillers, and Shades of Evil.  Most of these will scare young children and some adults.  I myself am using them with 2 tvs, 2 rokus, a couple projectors, and a chromecast.  We are currently missing Phantasms, Witching Hour, Night Stalkers, Jack-O'-Lantern Jamboree, Tricks and Treats, Creepy Crawlies 2, Blood Walls, Triple Thrill Pack.

As well as a few different holidays in the AtmosCHEERfx dvd.

Happy Halloween
